msgid ""
"KDE Menu Edit lets you edit how your apps are presented in application "
"launchers, such as Plasma's Application Launcher widget."
msgstr ""
"KDE Menu Edit vam omogoča urejanje, kako so aplikacije prikazane v "
"zaganjalnikih kot npr. gradnik Plasma's Application Launcher."
